gov.nasa.worldwindx.examples

Class ScankortDenmark

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.worldwindx.examples.ScankortDenmark

  • public class ScankortDenmark
extends java.lang.Object
    This example demonstrates high resolution imagery (0.2 meters per pixel) and elevation data (1.6 meters per pixel) served by the WorldWind WMS, and visualized by the WorldWind Java client.

    The data is from Denmark. Details for loading the imagery can be found in: config/Earth/ScankortDenmarkImageLayer.xml while information for loading the elevation data is in: config/Earth/ScankortDenmarkDSMElevationModel.xml.
